const _astro_dataLayerContent = [["Map",1,2,7,8,73,74],"meta::meta",["Map",3,4,5,6],"astro-version","5.0.9","config-digest","9800fc3cb7351302","portfolio",["Map",9,10,32,33,53,54],"ticomotor",{id:9,data:11,body:23,filePath:24,digest:25,rendered:26,legacyId:31},{title:12,description:13,client:14,year:15,tags:16,image:20,liveUrl:21,featured:22},"Sistema web para venta de autos","Aplicación web para compra y venta de autos en Costa Rica.","Ticomotor",2024,[17,18,19],"Rect","TailwindCSS","IA","/proyectos/website-ticomotor.png","https://ticomotor.es",true,"Ticomotor necesitaba una plataforma moderna que simplificara el proceso de compra y venta de vehículos en Costa Rica. Desarrollamos una aplicación web completa con catálogo de autos, filtros avanzados de búsqueda, fichas detalladas por vehículo y un sistema de contacto directo entre compradores y vendedores.\r\n\r\nLa integración de inteligencia artificial fue el elemento central del proyecto. Implementamos un asistente que ayuda a los usuarios a encontrar el vehículo ideal según su presupuesto, preferencias y necesidades, mejorando significativamente la experiencia de búsqueda y reduciendo el tiempo hasta la decisión de compra.\r\n\r\nLa plataforma se está posicionando rápidamente, aunque es bastente nueva, su estructura causa mucha confianza entre los usuarios.","src/content/portfolio/ticomotor.md","fb7aeb40502ce4f9",{html:27,metadata:28},"<p>Ticomotor necesitaba una plataforma moderna que simplificara el proceso de compra y venta de vehículos en Costa Rica. Desarrollamos una aplicación web completa con catálogo de autos, filtros avanzados de búsqueda, fichas detalladas por vehículo y un sistema de contacto directo entre compradores y vendedores.</p>\n<p>La integración de inteligencia artificial fue el elemento central del proyecto. Implementamos un asistente que ayuda a los usuarios a encontrar el vehículo ideal según su presupuesto, preferencias y necesidades, mejorando significativamente la experiencia de búsqueda y reduciendo el tiempo hasta la decisión de compra.</p>\n<p>La plataforma se está posicionando rápidamente, aunque es bastente nueva, su estructura causa mucha confianza entre los usuarios.</p>",{headings:29,imagePaths:30,frontmatter:11},[],[],"ticomotor.md","cabañas-don-ramiro",{id:32,data:34,body:44,filePath:45,digest:46,rendered:47,legacyId:52},{title:35,description:36,client:37,year:15,tags:38,image:42,liveUrl:43,featured:22},"Sitio web de reservas para hospedaje","Sitio web moderno con motor de reservar para cabañas don ramiro, sincroniza sus reservas con booking y airbnb.","Cabañas don Ramiro",[39,40,41],"Wordpress","Element","Bookings","/proyectos/website-donramiro.png","https://cabanasdonramiro.com","Cabañas Don Ramiro necesitaba una presencia digital que estuviera a la altura de la experiencia que ofrecen a sus huéspedes. Diseñamos y desarrollamos un sitio web moderno con un motor de reservas integrado que permite a los visitantes consultar disponibilidad y reservar directamente desde la web, sin intermediarios.\r\n\r\nLa sincronización automática con Booking.com y Airbnb fue el reto técnico central del proyecto. Implementamos una integración en tiempo real que mantiene el calendario de disponibilidad actualizado en todas las plataformas, eliminando el riesgo de reservas duplicadas y reduciendo el trabajo manual del equipo.\r\n\r\nEl resultado fue un aumento significativo en las reservas directas, reduciendo la dependencia de plataformas de terceros y mejorando el margen por reserva para el cliente.","src/content/portfolio/cabañas-don-ramiro.md","4a86fa6a76e65aac",{html:48,metadata:49},"<p>Cabañas Don Ramiro necesitaba una presencia digital que estuviera a la altura de la experiencia que ofrecen a sus huéspedes. Diseñamos y desarrollamos un sitio web moderno con un motor de reservas integrado que permite a los visitantes consultar disponibilidad y reservar directamente desde la web, sin intermediarios.</p>\n<p>La sincronización automática con Booking.com y Airbnb fue el reto técnico central del proyecto. Implementamos una integración en tiempo real que mantiene el calendario de disponibilidad actualizado en todas las plataformas, eliminando el riesgo de reservas duplicadas y reduciendo el trabajo manual del equipo.</p>\n<p>El resultado fue un aumento significativo en las reservas directas, reduciendo la dependencia de plataformas de terceros y mejorando el margen por reserva para el cliente.</p>",{headings:50,imagePaths:51,frontmatter:34},[],[],"cabañas-don-ramiro.md","tierras-gosen",{id:53,data:55,body:64,filePath:65,digest:66,rendered:67,legacyId:72},{title:56,description:57,client:58,year:59,tags:60,image:62,liveUrl:63,featured:22},"Sitio web - Café Gosen","Sitio web para Tierras Gosén, secciones de contacto, conectada a chatbot de whatsapp.","Tierras Gosén",2023,[39,40,61],"ManyChat","/proyectos/website-gosen.png","https://tierrasgosen.com/","Tierras Gosén quería un sitio web que reflejara la calidez de su marca y facilitara el contacto con sus clientes. Desarrollamos un sitio moderno con secciones claras de menú, historia del café y ubicación, priorizando una experiencia visual atractiva y una navegación intuitiva tanto en desktop como en móvil.\r\n\r\nLa integración con ManyChat fue el elemento diferenciador del proyecto. Conectamos el sitio con un chatbot de WhatsApp que responde automáticamente consultas frecuentes, toma pedidos y dirige a los usuarios al equipo de atención, disponible las 24 horas sin intervención manual.\r\n\r\nEl chatbot redujo significativamente el tiempo de respuesta a clientes y permitió al equipo de Tierras Gosén enfocarse en la operación del negocio mientras la automatización se encargaba de la comunicación digital.","src/content/portfolio/tierras-gosen.md","59e20af562eafd65",{html:68,metadata:69},"<p>Tierras Gosén quería un sitio web que reflejara la calidez de su marca y facilitara el contacto con sus clientes. Desarrollamos un sitio moderno con secciones claras de menú, historia del café y ubicación, priorizando una experiencia visual atractiva y una navegación intuitiva tanto en desktop como en móvil.</p>\n<p>La integración con ManyChat fue el elemento diferenciador del proyecto. Conectamos el sitio con un chatbot de WhatsApp que responde automáticamente consultas frecuentes, toma pedidos y dirige a los usuarios al equipo de atención, disponible las 24 horas sin intervención manual.</p>\n<p>El chatbot redujo significativamente el tiempo de respuesta a clientes y permitió al equipo de Tierras Gosén enfocarse en la operación del negocio mientras la automatización se encargaba de la comunicación digital.</p>",{headings:70,imagePaths:71,frontmatter:55},[],[],"tierras-gosen.md","blog",["Map",75,76,128,129,150,151,199,200,248,249,279,280,303,304],"unleash-creativity-with-these-cutting-edge-tablets",{id:75,data:77,body:88,filePath:89,digest:90,rendered:91,legacyId:127},{title:78,pubDate:79,author:80,authImage:81,image:82,tags:83,summary:86,type:87},"Unleash Creativity With These Cutting-Edge Tablets",["Date","2024-01-14T00:00:00.000Z"],"Bonnie Green","https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/avatars/bonnie-green.png","image5.png",[84,85],"tablets","gadgets","In the world of digital creativity, tablets have become indispensable tools for artists, designers, and anyone seeking to unleash their artistic potential.","Article","In the world of digital creativity, tablets have become indispensable tools for artists, designers, and anyone seeking to unleash their artistic potential. In 2024, the market is brimming with cutting-edge tablets that offer new dimensions of creativity. Let's dive into the exciting realm of tablet technology and discover the tools that can help you bring your artistic visions to life.\r\n\r\n## **1. Remarkable Displays**\r\n\r\nCutting-edge tablets feature remarkable displays with high resolutions, wide color gamuts, and exceptional brightness. Whether you're illustrating, editing photos, or 3D modeling, these displays provide true-to-life visuals and precise color accuracy.\r\n\r\n## **2. Powerful Processing Power**\r\n\r\nThe heart of a cutting-edge tablet is its processing power. With advanced processors and ample RAM, these tablets can handle resource-intensive tasks like rendering, video editing, and complex digital painting with ease.\r\n\r\n## **3. Innovative Stylus Technology**\r\n\r\nStylus technology has evolved significantly. Cutting-edge tablets come with styluses that offer precise control, pressure sensitivity, and low latency. They mimic the feel of traditional drawing and provide an intuitive creative experience.\r\n\r\n## **4. Versatile Software Compatibility**\r\n\r\nThese tablets are compatible with a wide range of creative software, from industry-standard programs like Adobe Creative Cloud to specialized apps for digital art, animation, and 3D modeling. You have the flexibility to choose the tools that suit your creative needs.\r\n\r\n## **5. 3D Modeling and Sculpting**\r\n\r\nFor those in the 3D modeling and sculpting realm, cutting-edge tablets support powerful applications that allow you to sculpt, texture, and animate your creations in a tactile and immersive way.\r\n\r\n## **6. Digital Painting and Illustration**\r\n\r\nArtists can explore a vast canvas of possibilities with digital painting and illustration. Cutting-edge tablets offer natural brush strokes, layers, and a variety of brushes to achieve stunning artistic results.\r\n\r\n## **7. Photo and Video Editing**\r\n\r\nPhotographers and videographers benefit from advanced tablets for on-the-go editing. High-resolution screens and touch-based controls make editing a breeze, whether you're enhancing photos or cutting video footage.\r\n\r\n## **8. Portability and Connectivity**\r\n\r\nCutting-edge tablets are designed for portability, making them ideal for creatives on the move. They offer a range of connectivity options, including USB-C, Bluetooth, and Wi-Fi, to streamline your workflow.\r\n\r\n## **9. Augmented Reality (AR)**\r\n\r\nSome cutting-edge tablets integrate augmented reality features, allowing artists to overlay digital creations onto the physical world, opening up new possibilities for interactive and immersive experiences.\r\n\r\n## **10. Cloud Integration**\r\n\r\nCloud integration ensures that your work is accessible from anywhere. You can sync your projects across devices and collaborate with others seamlessly.\r\n\r\nIn conclusion, if you're looking to unleash your creativity and take your digital artistry to new heights, cutting-edge tablets are your canvas. Their remarkable displays, powerful processing, and innovative stylus technology provide the tools you need to bring your creative visions to life. As we embark on the creative journey of 2024, explore the world of cutting-edge tablets and let your imagination soar.","src/content/blog/cutting-edge-tablets.md","115ade31990f9c14",{html:92,metadata:93},"<p>In the world of digital creativity, tablets have become indispensable tools for artists, designers, and anyone seeking to unleash their artistic potential. In 2024, the market is brimming with cutting-edge tablets that offer new dimensions of creativity. Let’s dive into the exciting realm of tablet technology and discover the tools that can help you bring your artistic visions to life.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-remarkable-displays\"><strong>1. Remarkable Displays</strong></h2>\n<p>Cutting-edge tablets feature remarkable displays with high resolutions, wide color gamuts, and exceptional brightness. Whether you’re illustrating, editing photos, or 3D modeling, these displays provide true-to-life visuals and precise color accuracy.</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-powerful-processing-power\"><strong>2. Powerful Processing Power</strong></h2>\n<p>The heart of a cutting-edge tablet is its processing power. With advanced processors and ample RAM, these tablets can handle resource-intensive tasks like rendering, video editing, and complex digital painting with ease.</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-innovative-stylus-technology\"><strong>3. Innovative Stylus Technology</strong></h2>\n<p>Stylus technology has evolved significantly. Cutting-edge tablets come with styluses that offer precise control, pressure sensitivity, and low latency. They mimic the feel of traditional drawing and provide an intuitive creative experience.</p>\n<h2 id=\"4-versatile-software-compatibility\"><strong>4. Versatile Software Compatibility</strong></h2>\n<p>These tablets are compatible with a wide range of creative software, from industry-standard programs like Adobe Creative Cloud to specialized apps for digital art, animation, and 3D modeling. You have the flexibility to choose the tools that suit your creative needs.</p>\n<h2 id=\"5-3d-modeling-and-sculpting\"><strong>5. 3D Modeling and Sculpting</strong></h2>\n<p>For those in the 3D modeling and sculpting realm, cutting-edge tablets support powerful applications that allow you to sculpt, texture, and animate your creations in a tactile and immersive way.</p>\n<h2 id=\"6-digital-painting-and-illustration\"><strong>6. Digital Painting and Illustration</strong></h2>\n<p>Artists can explore a vast canvas of possibilities with digital painting and illustration. Cutting-edge tablets offer natural brush strokes, layers, and a variety of brushes to achieve stunning artistic results.</p>\n<h2 id=\"7-photo-and-video-editing\"><strong>7. Photo and Video Editing</strong></h2>\n<p>Photographers and videographers benefit from advanced tablets for on-the-go editing. High-resolution screens and touch-based controls make editing a breeze, whether you’re enhancing photos or cutting video footage.</p>\n<h2 id=\"8-portability-and-connectivity\"><strong>8. Portability and Connectivity</strong></h2>\n<p>Cutting-edge tablets are designed for portability, making them ideal for creatives on the move. They offer a range of connectivity options, including USB-C, Bluetooth, and Wi-Fi, to streamline your workflow.</p>\n<h2 id=\"9-augmented-reality-ar\"><strong>9. Augmented Reality (AR)</strong></h2>\n<p>Some cutting-edge tablets integrate augmented reality features, allowing artists to overlay digital creations onto the physical world, opening up new possibilities for interactive and immersive experiences.</p>\n<h2 id=\"10-cloud-integration\"><strong>10. Cloud Integration</strong></h2>\n<p>Cloud integration ensures that your work is accessible from anywhere. You can sync your projects across devices and collaborate with others seamlessly.</p>\n<p>In conclusion, if you’re looking to unleash your creativity and take your digital artistry to new heights, cutting-edge tablets are your canvas. Their remarkable displays, powerful processing, and innovative stylus technology provide the tools you need to bring your creative visions to life. As we embark on the creative journey of 2024, explore the world of cutting-edge tablets and let your imagination soar.</p>",{headings:94,imagePaths:126,frontmatter:77},[95,99,102,105,108,111,114,117,120,123],{depth:96,slug:97,text:98},2,"1-remarkable-displays","1. Remarkable Displays",{depth:96,slug:100,text:101},"2-powerful-processing-power","2. Powerful Processing Power",{depth:96,slug:103,text:104},"3-innovative-stylus-technology","3. Innovative Stylus Technology",{depth:96,slug:106,text:107},"4-versatile-software-compatibility","4. Versatile Software Compatibility",{depth:96,slug:109,text:110},"5-3d-modeling-and-sculpting","5. 3D Modeling and Sculpting",{depth:96,slug:112,text:113},"6-digital-painting-and-illustration","6. Digital Painting and Illustration",{depth:96,slug:115,text:116},"7-photo-and-video-editing","7. Photo and Video Editing",{depth:96,slug:118,text:119},"8-portability-and-connectivity","8. Portability and Connectivity",{depth:96,slug:121,text:122},"9-augmented-reality-ar","9. Augmented Reality (AR)",{depth:96,slug:124,text:125},"10-cloud-integration","10. Cloud Integration",[],"cutting-edge-tablets.md","how-to-quickly-deploy-a-static-website",{id:128,data:130,body:141,filePath:142,digest:143,rendered:144,legacyId:149},{title:131,pubDate:132,author:133,authImage:134,image:135,tags:136,summary:139,type:140},"How to quickly deploy a static website",["Date","2024-01-20T00:00:00.000Z"],"Jese Leos","https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/avatars/jese-leos.png","image1.png",[137,138],"tech","hardware","Static websites are now used to bootstrap lots of websites and are becoming the basis for a variety of tools that even influence both web designers and developers influence both web designers and developers.","Tutorial","Static websites are now used to bootstrap lots of websites and are becoming the basis for a variety of tools that even influence both web designers and developers influence both web designers and developers. Static websites are now used to bootstrap lots of websites and are becoming the basis for a variety of tools that even influence both web designers and developers influence both web designers and developers. Static websites are now used to bootstrap lots of websites and are becoming the basis for a variety of tools that even influence both web designers and developers influence both web designers and developers. Static websites are now used to bootstrap lots of websites and are becoming the basis for a variety of tools that even influence both web designers and developers influence both web designers and developers. Static websites are now used to bootstrap lots of websites and are becoming the basis for a variety of tools that even influence both web designers and developers influence both web designers and developers.","src/content/blog/How to quickly deploy a static website.md","42a7d9b09fd394d0",{html:145,metadata:146},"<p>Static websites are now used to bootstrap lots of websites and are becoming the basis for a variety of tools that even influence both web designers and developers influence both web designers and developers. Static websites are now used to bootstrap lots of websites and are becoming the basis for a variety of tools that even influence both web designers and developers influence both web designers and developers. Static websites are now used to bootstrap lots of websites and are becoming the basis for a variety of tools that even influence both web designers and developers influence both web designers and developers. Static websites are now used to bootstrap lots of websites and are becoming the basis for a variety of tools that even influence both web designers and developers influence both web designers and developers. Static websites are now used to bootstrap lots of websites and are becoming the basis for a variety of tools that even influence both web designers and developers influence both web designers and developers.</p>",{headings:147,imagePaths:148,frontmatter:130},[],[],"How to quickly deploy a static website.md","capturing-lifes-moments-with-canon-excellence",{id:150,data:152,body:160,filePath:161,digest:162,rendered:163,legacyId:198},{title:153,pubDate:154,author:80,authImage:81,image:155,tags:156,summary:159,type:87},"Capturing Life's Moments with Canon Excellence",["Date","2024-01-15T00:00:00.000Z"],"image4.png",[157,158,137],"photography","canon","Canon has been a symbol of excellence in the world of photography for decades. In 2024, Canon continues to lead the way in innovation...","For photographers and enthusiasts alike, Canon has been a symbol of excellence in the world of photography for decades. In 2024, Canon continues to lead the way in innovation, enabling us to capture life's most precious moments with unparalleled quality and precision. Let's explore the world of photography and how Canon's excellence plays a pivotal role.\r\n\r\n## **1. Cutting-Edge Camera Technology**\r\n\r\nCanon is renowned for its cutting-edge camera technology. From DSLRs to mirrorless cameras, Canon consistently pushes the boundaries of what's possible in photography. High-resolution sensors, advanced autofocus systems, and remarkable image processing ensure that every shot is a masterpiece.\r\n\r\n## **2. Diverse Lens Ecosystem**\r\n\r\nCanon boasts a diverse and extensive lens ecosystem that caters to photographers of all levels. Whether you're into portrait photography, wildlife, or landscape, Canon offers a lens for every occasion. The L-series lenses are a testament to Canon's commitment to optical excellence.\r\n\r\n## **3. Innovative Imaging Solutions**\r\n\r\nCanon's imaging solutions extend beyond cameras and lenses. Their printers, scanners, and image editing software empower photographers to bring their vision to life. Canon's color accuracy and print quality are unmatched in the industry.\r\n\r\n## **4. Professional-Grade Video Recording**\r\n\r\nCanon cameras are not just for photography; they excel in videography too. From vlogging to cinematic filmmaking, Canon's video capabilities are a favorite among content creators. Dual Pixel Autofocus and high-quality 4K recording are staples of Canon's video prowess.\r\n\r\n## **5. Commitment to Sustainability**\r\n\r\nCanon is committed to environmental sustainability. They implement eco-friendly practices in manufacturing and recycling programs. Choosing Canon means supporting a company that cares about the planet.\r\n\r\n## **6. User-Friendly Interface**\r\n\r\nCanon's user-friendly interfaces make photography accessible to beginners and professionals alike. Intuitive menus, touchscreen controls, and customizable settings ensure a seamless shooting experience.\r\n\r\n## **7. Reliability and Durability**\r\n\r\nCanon's cameras are built to last. They can withstand challenging environments and offer durability that professional photographers demand. Canon users know they can rely on their gear in any situation.\r\n\r\n## **8. Photography Education**\r\n\r\nCanon supports photography education with workshops, tutorials, and online resources. They empower aspiring photographers to enhance their skills and make the most of Canon's equipment.\r\n\r\n## **9. Community and Inspiration**\r\n\r\nCanon's photography community is vibrant and inspiring. Photographers share their work, tips, and experiences, creating a sense of camaraderie among enthusiasts and professionals.\r\n\r\n## **10. Innovation in the Digital Era**\r\n\r\nIn a rapidly evolving digital era, Canon consistently adapts and innovates. They embrace new technologies like AI and connectivity to enhance the photographic experience.\r\n\r\nIn conclusion, Canon's commitment to excellence in photography is unwavering. Whether you're a professional photographer, an aspiring enthusiast, or someone who simply loves capturing life's moments, Canon's technology and innovation empower you to do so","src/content/blog/cannon-excellence.md","72e0f9be4b69d71f",{html:164,metadata:165},"<p>For photographers and enthusiasts alike, Canon has been a symbol of excellence in the world of photography for decades. In 2024, Canon continues to lead the way in innovation, enabling us to capture life’s most precious moments with unparalleled quality and precision. Let’s explore the world of photography and how Canon’s excellence plays a pivotal role.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-cutting-edge-camera-technology\"><strong>1. Cutting-Edge Camera Technology</strong></h2>\n<p>Canon is renowned for its cutting-edge camera technology. From DSLRs to mirrorless cameras, Canon consistently pushes the boundaries of what’s possible in photography. High-resolution sensors, advanced autofocus systems, and remarkable image processing ensure that every shot is a masterpiece.</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-diverse-lens-ecosystem\"><strong>2. Diverse Lens Ecosystem</strong></h2>\n<p>Canon boasts a diverse and extensive lens ecosystem that caters to photographers of all levels. Whether you’re into portrait photography, wildlife, or landscape, Canon offers a lens for every occasion. The L-series lenses are a testament to Canon’s commitment to optical excellence.</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-innovative-imaging-solutions\"><strong>3. Innovative Imaging Solutions</strong></h2>\n<p>Canon’s imaging solutions extend beyond cameras and lenses. Their printers, scanners, and image editing software empower photographers to bring their vision to life. Canon’s color accuracy and print quality are unmatched in the industry.</p>\n<h2 id=\"4-professional-grade-video-recording\"><strong>4. Professional-Grade Video Recording</strong></h2>\n<p>Canon cameras are not just for photography; they excel in videography too. From vlogging to cinematic filmmaking, Canon’s video capabilities are a favorite among content creators. Dual Pixel Autofocus and high-quality 4K recording are staples of Canon’s video prowess.</p>\n<h2 id=\"5-commitment-to-sustainability\"><strong>5. Commitment to Sustainability</strong></h2>\n<p>Canon is committed to environmental sustainability. They implement eco-friendly practices in manufacturing and recycling programs. Choosing Canon means supporting a company that cares about the planet.</p>\n<h2 id=\"6-user-friendly-interface\"><strong>6. User-Friendly Interface</strong></h2>\n<p>Canon’s user-friendly interfaces make photography accessible to beginners and professionals alike. Intuitive menus, touchscreen controls, and customizable settings ensure a seamless shooting experience.</p>\n<h2 id=\"7-reliability-and-durability\"><strong>7. Reliability and Durability</strong></h2>\n<p>Canon’s cameras are built to last. They can withstand challenging environments and offer durability that professional photographers demand. Canon users know they can rely on their gear in any situation.</p>\n<h2 id=\"8-photography-education\"><strong>8. Photography Education</strong></h2>\n<p>Canon supports photography education with workshops, tutorials, and online resources. They empower aspiring photographers to enhance their skills and make the most of Canon’s equipment.</p>\n<h2 id=\"9-community-and-inspiration\"><strong>9. Community and Inspiration</strong></h2>\n<p>Canon’s photography community is vibrant and inspiring. Photographers share their work, tips, and experiences, creating a sense of camaraderie among enthusiasts and professionals.</p>\n<h2 id=\"10-innovation-in-the-digital-era\"><strong>10. Innovation in the Digital Era</strong></h2>\n<p>In a rapidly evolving digital era, Canon consistently adapts and innovates. They embrace new technologies like AI and connectivity to enhance the photographic experience.</p>\n<p>In conclusion, Canon’s commitment to excellence in photography is unwavering. Whether you’re a professional photographer, an aspiring enthusiast, or someone who simply loves capturing life’s moments, Canon’s technology and innovation empower you to do so</p>",{headings:166,imagePaths:197,frontmatter:152},[167,170,173,176,179,182,185,188,191,194],{depth:96,slug:168,text:169},"1-cutting-edge-camera-technology","1. Cutting-Edge Camera Technology",{depth:96,slug:171,text:172},"2-diverse-lens-ecosystem","2. Diverse Lens Ecosystem",{depth:96,slug:174,text:175},"3-innovative-imaging-solutions","3. Innovative Imaging Solutions",{depth:96,slug:177,text:178},"4-professional-grade-video-recording","4. Professional-Grade Video Recording",{depth:96,slug:180,text:181},"5-commitment-to-sustainability","5. Commitment to Sustainability",{depth:96,slug:183,text:184},"6-user-friendly-interface","6. User-Friendly Interface",{depth:96,slug:186,text:187},"7-reliability-and-durability","7. Reliability and Durability",{depth:96,slug:189,text:190},"8-photography-education","8. Photography Education",{depth:96,slug:192,text:193},"9-community-and-inspiration","9. Community and Inspiration",{depth:96,slug:195,text:196},"10-innovation-in-the-digital-era","10. Innovation in the Digital Era",[],"cannon-excellence.md","elevate-your-mobile-experience-with-samsung",{id:199,data:201,body:209,filePath:210,digest:211,rendered:212,legacyId:247},{title:202,pubDate:203,author:80,authImage:81,image:204,tags:205,summary:208,type:87},"Our first project with Astro",["Date","2024-01-17T00:00:00.000Z"],"image3.png",[206,207,85],"samsung","smartphones","In the ever-evolving world of mobile technology, Samsung has consistently delivered cutting-edge devices that redefine the way we experience the digital world.","In the ever-evolving world of mobile technology, Samsung has consistently delivered cutting-edge devices that redefine the way we experience the digital world. If you're looking to elevate your mobile experience in 2024, here's why Samsung should be at the top of your list.\r\n\r\n## **1. Innovative Display Technology**\r\n\r\nSamsung's mobile devices are renowned for their stunning displays. With advancements in AMOLED and Dynamic AMOLED technology, Samsung offers vibrant colors, deep blacks, and sharp resolutions. Whether you're streaming videos, playing games, or working on productivity apps, the visual experience is unparalleled.\r\n\r\n## **2. Powerful Performance**\r\n\r\nSamsung equips its smartphones with powerful processors and ample RAM, ensuring smooth multitasking and efficient performance. Whether you're a mobile gamer, content creator, or business professional, Samsung devices can handle your tasks with ease.\r\n\r\n## **3. Impressive Camera Systems**\r\n\r\nCapture life's moments in stunning detail with Samsung's camera systems. From high-resolution main cameras to ultra-wide and telephoto lenses, Samsung devices provide versatile photography options. Features like AI enhancements and night mode deliver exceptional results in various lighting conditions.\r\n\r\n## **4. 5G Connectivity**\r\n\r\nStay at the forefront of connectivity with 5G-enabled Samsung devices. Enjoy lightning-fast download and upload speeds, low latency, and seamless streaming. Whether you're working remotely or enjoying online entertainment, 5G ensures a lag-free experience.\r\n\r\n## **5. Long-lasting Battery Life**\r\n\r\nSamsung understands the importance of battery life. Their devices come equipped with large batteries that can last all day. With optimizations for power efficiency and fast charging capabilities, you can stay connected without interruptions.\r\n\r\n## **6. Secure and User-Friendly**\r\n\r\nSamsung prioritizes security with features like Samsung Knox, ensuring your data is protected. Additionally, their user-friendly interface, One UI, offers a smooth and intuitive user experience.\r\n\r\n## **7. Ecosystem Integration**\r\n\r\nIf you're already part of the Samsung ecosystem, their devices seamlessly integrate with each other. Share content across devices, sync your data, and enjoy a cohesive digital experience.\r\n\r\n## **8. Ongoing Software Support**\r\n\r\nSamsung provides regular software updates and security patches to keep your device running smoothly and protected from potential vulnerabilities.\r\n\r\n## **9. Eco-Friendly Initiatives**\r\n\r\nSamsung is committed to sustainability. They strive to reduce their environmental footprint by using eco-friendly materials and implementing recycling programs.\r\n\r\n## **10. Wide Range of Options**\r\n\r\nSamsung offers a wide range of devices to cater to various needs and budgets. Whether you prefer flagship models or more budget-friendly options, there's a Samsung device for you.\r\n\r\nIn conclusion, if you're looking to elevate your mobile experience in 2024, Samsung should be your go-to choice. Their commitment to innovation, performance, and user satisfaction makes them a leader in the mobile technology industry. Explore the Samsung ecosystem and discover how it can enhance your digital lifestyle.","src/content/blog/elevate-your-mobile-experience.md","c1d2c87f399a5887",{html:213,metadata:214},"<p>In the ever-evolving world of mobile technology, Samsung has consistently delivered cutting-edge devices that redefine the way we experience the digital world. If you’re looking to elevate your mobile experience in 2024, here’s why Samsung should be at the top of your list.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-innovative-display-technology\"><strong>1. Innovative Display Technology</strong></h2>\n<p>Samsung’s mobile devices are renowned for their stunning displays. With advancements in AMOLED and Dynamic AMOLED technology, Samsung offers vibrant colors, deep blacks, and sharp resolutions. Whether you’re streaming videos, playing games, or working on productivity apps, the visual experience is unparalleled.</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-powerful-performance\"><strong>2. Powerful Performance</strong></h2>\n<p>Samsung equips its smartphones with powerful processors and ample RAM, ensuring smooth multitasking and efficient performance. Whether you’re a mobile gamer, content creator, or business professional, Samsung devices can handle your tasks with ease.</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-impressive-camera-systems\"><strong>3. Impressive Camera Systems</strong></h2>\n<p>Capture life’s moments in stunning detail with Samsung’s camera systems. From high-resolution main cameras to ultra-wide and telephoto lenses, Samsung devices provide versatile photography options. Features like AI enhancements and night mode deliver exceptional results in various lighting conditions.</p>\n<h2 id=\"4-5g-connectivity\"><strong>4. 5G Connectivity</strong></h2>\n<p>Stay at the forefront of connectivity with 5G-enabled Samsung devices. Enjoy lightning-fast download and upload speeds, low latency, and seamless streaming. Whether you’re working remotely or enjoying online entertainment, 5G ensures a lag-free experience.</p>\n<h2 id=\"5-long-lasting-battery-life\"><strong>5. Long-lasting Battery Life</strong></h2>\n<p>Samsung understands the importance of battery life. Their devices come equipped with large batteries that can last all day. With optimizations for power efficiency and fast charging capabilities, you can stay connected without interruptions.</p>\n<h2 id=\"6-secure-and-user-friendly\"><strong>6. Secure and User-Friendly</strong></h2>\n<p>Samsung prioritizes security with features like Samsung Knox, ensuring your data is protected. Additionally, their user-friendly interface, One UI, offers a smooth and intuitive user experience.</p>\n<h2 id=\"7-ecosystem-integration\"><strong>7. Ecosystem Integration</strong></h2>\n<p>If you’re already part of the Samsung ecosystem, their devices seamlessly integrate with each other. Share content across devices, sync your data, and enjoy a cohesive digital experience.</p>\n<h2 id=\"8-ongoing-software-support\"><strong>8. Ongoing Software Support</strong></h2>\n<p>Samsung provides regular software updates and security patches to keep your device running smoothly and protected from potential vulnerabilities.</p>\n<h2 id=\"9-eco-friendly-initiatives\"><strong>9. Eco-Friendly Initiatives</strong></h2>\n<p>Samsung is committed to sustainability. They strive to reduce their environmental footprint by using eco-friendly materials and implementing recycling programs.</p>\n<h2 id=\"10-wide-range-of-options\"><strong>10. Wide Range of Options</strong></h2>\n<p>Samsung offers a wide range of devices to cater to various needs and budgets. Whether you prefer flagship models or more budget-friendly options, there’s a Samsung device for you.</p>\n<p>In conclusion, if you’re looking to elevate your mobile experience in 2024, Samsung should be your go-to choice. Their commitment to innovation, performance, and user satisfaction makes them a leader in the mobile technology industry. Explore the Samsung ecosystem and discover how it can enhance your digital lifestyle.</p>",{headings:215,imagePaths:246,frontmatter:201},[216,219,222,225,228,231,234,237,240,243],{depth:96,slug:217,text:218},"1-innovative-display-technology","1. Innovative Display Technology",{depth:96,slug:220,text:221},"2-powerful-performance","2. Powerful Performance",{depth:96,slug:223,text:224},"3-impressive-camera-systems","3. Impressive Camera Systems",{depth:96,slug:226,text:227},"4-5g-connectivity","4. 5G Connectivity",{depth:96,slug:229,text:230},"5-long-lasting-battery-life","5. Long-lasting Battery Life",{depth:96,slug:232,text:233},"6-secure-and-user-friendly","6. Secure and User-Friendly",{depth:96,slug:235,text:236},"7-ecosystem-integration","7. Ecosystem Integration",{depth:96,slug:238,text:239},"8-ongoing-software-support","8. Ongoing Software Support",{depth:96,slug:241,text:242},"9-eco-friendly-initiatives","9. Eco-Friendly Initiatives",{depth:96,slug:244,text:245},"10-wide-range-of-options","10. Wide Range of Options",[],"elevate-your-mobile-experience.md","cabanas-don-ramiro-caso-de-exito",{id:248,data:250,body:261,filePath:262,digest:263,rendered:264,legacyId:278},{title:251,pubDate:252,author:253,authImage:254,image:42,tags:255,slug:248,summary:260,type:87},"Cómo aumentamos las reservas directas de Cabañas Don Ramiro con un sitio web propio",["Date","2024-03-10T00:00:00.000Z"],"Pimenta Studio","/Logo.svg",[256,257,258,259],"wordpress","reservas","turismo","caso-de-exito","Cabañas Don Ramiro dependía completamente de Booking y Airbnb para sus reservas. Desarrollamos un sitio web con motor de reservas propio que sincroniza con ambas plataformas y aumentó sus reservas directas significativamente.","## El reto\r\n\r\nCabañas Don Ramiro es un hospedaje familiar ubicado en una zona turística de Costa Rica. Como muchos negocios del sector, dependían casi exclusivamente de plataformas como Booking.com y Airbnb para recibir reservas. Esto significaba pagar comisiones de entre 15% y 20% por cada reserva, sin control sobre la experiencia del cliente ni la posibilidad de fidelizarlo directamente.\r\n\r\nEl equipo nos contactó con un objetivo claro: quería tener su propio canal de ventas digital que le permitiera recibir reservas directas, reducir la dependencia de terceros y proyectar una imagen más profesional.\r\n\r\n## La solución\r\n\r\nDiseñamos y desarrollamos un sitio web moderno con identidad visual propia, construido sobre WordPress con Elementor para facilitar la gestión de contenido por parte del equipo sin necesidad de conocimientos técnicos.\r\n\r\nEl elemento central fue la integración de un motor de reservas que permite a los visitantes:\r\n\r\n- Consultar disponibilidad en tiempo real\r\n- Seleccionar fechas y tipo de cabaña\r\n- Completar la reserva y el pago directamente en el sitio\r\n\r\nLo más importante fue la **sincronización bidireccional con Booking.com y Airbnb**. Cualquier reserva recibida en cualquiera de las tres plataformas actualiza automáticamente el calendario en todas las demás, eliminando el riesgo de overbooking.\r\n\r\n## El resultado\r\n\r\nDesde el lanzamiento del sitio, Cabañas Don Ramiro comenzó a recibir reservas directas de forma constante, reduciendo su dependencia de plataformas de terceros y mejorando el margen por reserva al eliminar las comisiones intermediarias.\r\n\r\nEl sitio también mejoró su posicionamiento en búsquedas locales, atrayendo visitantes que buscaban hospedaje en la zona directamente desde Google.\r\n\r\n> \"Antes todo pasaba por Booking. Ahora tenemos nuestro propio canal y los clientes nos escriben directamente. Fue una de las mejores inversiones que hemos hecho.\" — Equipo Cabañas Don Ramiro","src/content/blog/cabanas-don-ramiro-caso-de-exito.md","31b2aa071ee6c5fb",{html:265,metadata:266},"<h2 id=\"el-reto\">El reto</h2>\n<p>Cabañas Don Ramiro es un hospedaje familiar ubicado en una zona turística de Costa Rica. Como muchos negocios del sector, dependían casi exclusivamente de plataformas como Booking.com y Airbnb para recibir reservas. Esto significaba pagar comisiones de entre 15% y 20% por cada reserva, sin control sobre la experiencia del cliente ni la posibilidad de fidelizarlo directamente.</p>\n<p>El equipo nos contactó con un objetivo claro: quería tener su propio canal de ventas digital que le permitiera recibir reservas directas, reducir la dependencia de terceros y proyectar una imagen más profesional.</p>\n<h2 id=\"la-solución\">La solución</h2>\n<p>Diseñamos y desarrollamos un sitio web moderno con identidad visual propia, construido sobre WordPress con Elementor para facilitar la gestión de contenido por parte del equipo sin necesidad de conocimientos técnicos.</p>\n<p>El elemento central fue la integración de un motor de reservas que permite a los visitantes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Consultar disponibilidad en tiempo real</li>\n<li>Seleccionar fechas y tipo de cabaña</li>\n<li>Completar la reserva y el pago directamente en el sitio</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Lo más importante fue la <strong>sincronización bidireccional con Booking.com y Airbnb</strong>. Cualquier reserva recibida en cualquiera de las tres plataformas actualiza automáticamente el calendario en todas las demás, eliminando el riesgo de overbooking.</p>\n<h2 id=\"el-resultado\">El resultado</h2>\n<p>Desde el lanzamiento del sitio, Cabañas Don Ramiro comenzó a recibir reservas directas de forma constante, reduciendo su dependencia de plataformas de terceros y mejorando el margen por reserva al eliminar las comisiones intermediarias.</p>\n<p>El sitio también mejoró su posicionamiento en búsquedas locales, atrayendo visitantes que buscaban hospedaje en la zona directamente desde Google.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“Antes todo pasaba por Booking. Ahora tenemos nuestro propio canal y los clientes nos escriben directamente. Fue una de las mejores inversiones que hemos hecho.” — Equipo Cabañas Don Ramiro</p>\n</blockquote>",{headings:267,imagePaths:277,frontmatter:250},[268,271,274],{depth:96,slug:269,text:270},"el-reto","El reto",{depth:96,slug:272,text:273},"la-solución","La solución",{depth:96,slug:275,text:276},"el-resultado","El resultado",[],"cabanas-don-ramiro-caso-de-exito.md","ticomotor-caso-de-exito",{id:279,data:281,body:291,filePath:292,digest:293,rendered:294,legacyId:302},{title:282,pubDate:283,author:253,authImage:254,image:284,tags:285,summary:290,type:87},"Ticomotor: construyendo el marketplace de autos más moderno de Costa Rica",["Date","2024-05-15T00:00:00.000Z"],"/proyectos/ticomotor-web.png",[286,287,288,289,259],"react","tailwindcss","inteligencia-artificial","marketplace","Desarrollamos para Ticomotor una aplicación web de compra y venta de autos con inteligencia artificial integrada, ofreciendo una experiencia muy superior a los clasificados tradicionales del mercado costarricense.","## El reto\r\n\r\nEl mercado de compra y venta de autos en Costa Rica estaba dominado por clasificados tradicionales con interfaces desactualizadas, poca información de los vehículos y sin herramientas que ayudaran al comprador a tomar una decisión informada.\r\n\r\nTicomotor llegó con una visión clara: crear una plataforma moderna que pusiera al comprador en el centro, con información completa, búsqueda inteligente y una experiencia de usuario que estuviera a la altura de los mejores marketplaces internacionales.\r\n\r\n## La solución\r\n\r\nConstruimos una aplicación web completa con React y TailwindCSS, diseñada desde cero para ser rápida, responsiva y fácil de usar tanto para compradores como para vendedores.\r\n\r\nLas funcionalidades principales incluyen:\r\n\r\n- **Catálogo completo** con fichas detalladas por vehículo: fotos, especificaciones técnicas, historial y precio\r\n- **Filtros avanzados** por marca, modelo, año, precio, kilometraje y tipo de combustible\r\n- **Sistema de contacto directo** entre compradores y vendedores sin intermediarios\r\n\r\nEl elemento diferenciador fue la integración de **inteligencia artificial** como asistente de búsqueda. El usuario puede describir en lenguaje natural lo que busca (\"un SUV familiar con menos de 50,000 km y menos de $20,000\") y el sistema interpreta la consulta y muestra los vehículos más relevantes.\r\n\r\n## El resultado\r\n\r\nTicomotor se posicionó rápidamente como una referencia en el mercado automotriz costarricense, ofreciendo una experiencia de usuario muy superior a los clasificados tradicionales.\r\n\r\nLa plataforma genera un alto volumen de contactos calificados para los vendedores, ya que los compradores llegan con información completa y una intención de compra clara, reduciendo el ciclo de venta.\r\n\r\n> \"Queríamos hacer algo diferente en el mercado de autos de Costa Rica. Pimenta Studio entendió exactamente la visión y la ejecutó.\" — Equipo Ticomotor","src/content/blog/ticomotor-caso-de-exito.md","14aa62e852b81290",{html:295,metadata:296},"<h2 id=\"el-reto\">El reto</h2>\n<p>El mercado de compra y venta de autos en Costa Rica estaba dominado por clasificados tradicionales con interfaces desactualizadas, poca información de los vehículos y sin herramientas que ayudaran al comprador a tomar una decisión informada.</p>\n<p>Ticomotor llegó con una visión clara: crear una plataforma moderna que pusiera al comprador en el centro, con información completa, búsqueda inteligente y una experiencia de usuario que estuviera a la altura de los mejores marketplaces internacionales.</p>\n<h2 id=\"la-solución\">La solución</h2>\n<p>Construimos una aplicación web completa con React y TailwindCSS, diseñada desde cero para ser rápida, responsiva y fácil de usar tanto para compradores como para vendedores.</p>\n<p>Las funcionalidades principales incluyen:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Catálogo completo</strong> con fichas detalladas por vehículo: fotos, especificaciones técnicas, historial y precio</li>\n<li><strong>Filtros avanzados</strong> por marca, modelo, año, precio, kilometraje y tipo de combustible</li>\n<li><strong>Sistema de contacto directo</strong> entre compradores y vendedores sin intermediarios</li>\n</ul>\n<p>El elemento diferenciador fue la integración de <strong>inteligencia artificial</strong> como asistente de búsqueda. El usuario puede describir en lenguaje natural lo que busca (“un SUV familiar con menos de 50,000 km y menos de $20,000”) y el sistema interpreta la consulta y muestra los vehículos más relevantes.</p>\n<h2 id=\"el-resultado\">El resultado</h2>\n<p>Ticomotor se posicionó rápidamente como una referencia en el mercado automotriz costarricense, ofreciendo una experiencia de usuario muy superior a los clasificados tradicionales.</p>\n<p>La plataforma genera un alto volumen de contactos calificados para los vendedores, ya que los compradores llegan con información completa y una intención de compra clara, reduciendo el ciclo de venta.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“Queríamos hacer algo diferente en el mercado de autos de Costa Rica. Pimenta Studio entendió exactamente la visión y la ejecutó.” — Equipo Ticomotor</p>\n</blockquote>",{headings:297,imagePaths:301,frontmatter:281},[298,299,300],{depth:96,slug:269,text:270},{depth:96,slug:272,text:273},{depth:96,slug:275,text:276},[],"ticomotor-caso-de-exito.md","tierras-gosen-caso-de-exito",{id:303,data:305,body:314,filePath:315,digest:316,rendered:317,legacyId:325},{title:306,pubDate:307,author:253,authImage:254,image:308,tags:309,summary:313,type:87},"Tierras Gosén: automatizando la atención al cliente con un chatbot de WhatsApp",["Date","2024-01-20T00:00:00.000Z"],"/proyectos/gosen-web.png",[256,310,311,312,259],"chatbot","whatsapp","automatizacion","Para Tierras Gosén desarrollamos un sitio web conectado a un chatbot de WhatsApp que responde consultas, toma pedidos y atiende clientes las 24 horas sin intervención manual.","## El reto\r\n\r\nTierras Gosén es un café costarricense con una comunidad fiel de clientes. Su equipo recibía decenas de mensajes diarios por WhatsApp con preguntas sobre el menú, horarios, ubicación y pedidos especiales. Responder manualmente cada mensaje consumía tiempo valioso que el equipo necesitaba para operar el negocio.\r\n\r\nAdemás, no tenían presencia web formal. Sus clientes los encontraban principalmente por recomendación o redes sociales, pero no había un lugar centralizado con toda la información del negocio.\r\n\r\n## La solución\r\n\r\nDesarrollamos un sitio web limpio y atractivo que refleja la identidad cálida de la marca, con secciones de menú, historia, galería, ubicación y contacto.\r\n\r\nLa pieza diferenciadora fue la integración con **ManyChat** para crear un chatbot de WhatsApp que:\r\n\r\n- Responde automáticamente preguntas frecuentes (horarios, ubicación, menú)\r\n- Guía al usuario a través de un flujo para hacer pedidos especiales\r\n- Escala a un agente humano cuando la consulta lo requiere\r\n- Está disponible las 24 horas, los 7 días de la semana\r\n\r\nEl chatbot se conecta directamente al número de WhatsApp Business del negocio, por lo que los clientes interactúan en el canal que ya usan sin necesidad de descargar ninguna app adicional.\r\n\r\n## El resultado\r\n\r\nDesde la implementación, el equipo de Tierras Gosén redujo significativamente el tiempo dedicado a responder mensajes repetitivos. El chatbot maneja la mayoría de las consultas de forma autónoma, liberando al equipo para enfocarse en la operación del café.\r\n\r\nLos clientes valoran la respuesta inmediata, especialmente fuera del horario de atención, y el negocio ha visto un aumento en pedidos especiales gracias al flujo guiado del chatbot.\r\n\r\n> \"Antes pasábamos horas respondiendo los mismos mensajes. Ahora el bot lo hace solo y nosotros nos enfocamos en el café.\" — Equipo Tierras Gosén","src/content/blog/tierras-gosen-caso-de-exito.md","a92faa51d507b733",{html:318,metadata:319},"<h2 id=\"el-reto\">El reto</h2>\n<p>Tierras Gosén es un café costarricense con una comunidad fiel de clientes. Su equipo recibía decenas de mensajes diarios por WhatsApp con preguntas sobre el menú, horarios, ubicación y pedidos especiales. Responder manualmente cada mensaje consumía tiempo valioso que el equipo necesitaba para operar el negocio.</p>\n<p>Además, no tenían presencia web formal. Sus clientes los encontraban principalmente por recomendación o redes sociales, pero no había un lugar centralizado con toda la información del negocio.</p>\n<h2 id=\"la-solución\">La solución</h2>\n<p>Desarrollamos un sitio web limpio y atractivo que refleja la identidad cálida de la marca, con secciones de menú, historia, galería, ubicación y contacto.</p>\n<p>La pieza diferenciadora fue la integración con <strong>ManyChat</strong> para crear un chatbot de WhatsApp que:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Responde automáticamente preguntas frecuentes (horarios, ubicación, menú)</li>\n<li>Guía al usuario a través de un flujo para hacer pedidos especiales</li>\n<li>Escala a un agente humano cuando la consulta lo requiere</li>\n<li>Está disponible las 24 horas, los 7 días de la semana</li>\n</ul>\n<p>El chatbot se conecta directamente al número de WhatsApp Business del negocio, por lo que los clientes interactúan en el canal que ya usan sin necesidad de descargar ninguna app adicional.</p>\n<h2 id=\"el-resultado\">El resultado</h2>\n<p>Desde la implementación, el equipo de Tierras Gosén redujo significativamente el tiempo dedicado a responder mensajes repetitivos. El chatbot maneja la mayoría de las consultas de forma autónoma, liberando al equipo para enfocarse en la operación del café.</p>\n<p>Los clientes valoran la respuesta inmediata, especialmente fuera del horario de atención, y el negocio ha visto un aumento en pedidos especiales gracias al flujo guiado del chatbot.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“Antes pasábamos horas respondiendo los mismos mensajes. Ahora el bot lo hace solo y nosotros nos enfocamos en el café.” — Equipo Tierras Gosén</p>\n</blockquote>",{headings:320,imagePaths:324,frontmatter:305},[321,322,323],{depth:96,slug:269,text:270},{depth:96,slug:272,text:273},{depth:96,slug:275,text:276},[],"tierras-gosen-caso-de-exito.md"];

